title: NFL Around the League: AFC West - August 21st, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: AFC West - August 21st, 2013
description:
Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling talk fantasy football, the latest NFL headlines and preview the AFC West. Will Wesseling lose his Oakland Raiders bet and eat his softball pants? Tell us your thoughts on Twitter @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.
